  <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;A room can completely change if you’ve got the right lighting in it. Twinkling lights are the bomb. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;We can easily forgive a child who is afraid of the dark; the real tragedy of life is when men are afraid of the light.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

